{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Spikerz! uses player-hosted multiplayer sessions, so a stable internet connection is essential for the best experience.</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786900/extras/welcome.gif?t=1728238888\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up and compete against players online in intense volleyball matches ranging from 2 to 12 players! Take full control of your character, dig, set, spike, and block your way to victory and climb the ranks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Easy to Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Spikerz! features simple, easy-to-learn controls with endless gameplay possibilities! Each match is a unique experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Become the Best</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose your position and stats before each match, balancing speed, power, and jump. Find the perfect combination and become a devastating Spikerz!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cooperate to Dominate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Spikerz! supports matches from 1v1 to 6v6. You won\u2019t always be alone on your team, so work together and become a formidable team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786900/extras/WISHLIST.png?t=1728238888\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728238888","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786900/page.bg.jpg?t=1728238888","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786900/885a640a4199e56014e943129c434a61020ac0a8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=172